.ue 1
                                                                       $.#$
                                                            Calw 15th April
My dear Herman

.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: 15th April
This is but a small note to express you my wishes and prayers on your
birthday. You have experienced during these 23 years much merci and long
suffring of the Lord, and We say with you Glory and honour to God for His
Grace. May you every day more experience what it is that to live from
Grace, So die to self that grace may be magnified, so small in your own
eyes that the Lord may be great in you and use you for His work.

Adieu dear Herman. Grace and peace be with you
.fo -
                                               Yours Julie Gundert


